text: Ulac u$ilif fellawen, ma tennam d a pxevbem tilawin, ne$ ma teffrem. Ieoa Oebbi, ar tesmektayem tent id. Maca, ur asent aahdet, di tbavnit, siwa ma tennam awal uwqim. Ur ferrut $ef lemlak, alamma ibbwev lajel iuran. Cfut ar Oebbi Ieoa i illan degwen. Eadret iman nnwen segS. Cfut ar Oebbi Ipsemmie, Ieellem
